data.description:
VA LOW Interest Rate Assumable LOAN!!!!!
Welcome to your new home in Maricopa, Arizona! This stunning, newly constructed residence is a 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom gem that exudes modern luxury and comfort. Nestled conveniently across from the green belt, this well-appointed home features a thoughtfully designed split floor plan that's perfect for contemporary living.

As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the heart of the home, a gourmet kitchen that will delight any chef. It boasts a high-end gas range, sleek stainless steel appliances, and light-colored granite countertops that beautifully complement the rich cabinetry. 

The kitchen also features an inviting island, perfect for all your entertaining needs, whether you're hosting a dinner party or enjoying a cozy breakfast. The spacious master bedroom is your private oasis, complete with an en suite bathroom that includes a generously sized walk-in closet, dual vanities, and a sizable shower. This master suite offers the perfect retreat after a long day.

Built in 2021, this home is in pristine condition and has been gently lived in, making it the ideal opportunity for those seeking a turnkey property. It's not only a beautiful place to call home but also situated in a fantastic location, with the green belt just steps away, providing a picturesque backdrop and an excellent area for outdoor activities and leisure.
